snippet.textDisplay: One of my friends caught Covid twice. For him, it was mild. Another friend though... she's still dealing with the long term effects of it. She and her family are unfortunatly long-term haulers. I've had so many friends and family get sick or die of this virus. It's absolutely horrible.
